Author: tinypotheadprincess
Text: If you haven't eaten in that long, it really is best for you to have something. I suggest you get something like soup because those are normally light and really low cal, and tell your teacher or whoever that you aren't feeling very well. It'll also give you some salt and other electrolytes to help keep your body going.

Author: mrsnoire
Text: Take electrolites with you and blame stomach flu
